<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM1.6.2">
<l>matuvār taṇṇan tuḻāyāṉ</l>
<l>mutuvē tamutalvaṉuk</l>
<l>ketuvē teṉpaṇi yeṉṉā</l>
<l>tatuvē yāṭceyyu mīṭē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>For the one with the honey-flowing cool Tulsi,</l>
<l>him who is the first in the ancient Vedas,</l>
<l>without saying “what is the cause, which is the service”,</l>
<l>that alone is the application that makes one a servant.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
